  "description": "Celebrate milestone birthdays in unforgettable style on Lake Travis! Perfect for 30th, 40th, 50th, 60th+ birthdays with 14-75 guests, professional service, and memories to last a lifetime. Milestone birthdays deserve exceptional celebrations! Whether turning 30, 40, 50, 60, or beyond, a Lake Travis cruise creates the perfect atmosphere to honor life's special moments with the people who matter most. Professional captain and crew, premium sound for birthday playlists and speeches, flexible format for mingling and celebrating, surprise-friendly - we'll help coordinate, champagne toasts and celebration moments, photo opportunities with birthday honoree, customizable party decorations and themes, swimming and floating (weather permitting), BYOB or full bar service, catered meals coordination, combines elegance with fun, creates unforgettable memories. Fleet for all celebration sizes: Day Tripper (14 guests intimate, $195/hr), Me Seeks the Irony (25 guests, $295/hr), Clever Girl (50-75 guests big celebration, $495/hr). Popular formats: 3-4 hours, often sunset timing for special atmosphere. Packages: Standard cruise, Essentials (+$100-200/hr), Ultimate (+$250-350/hr recommended for milestones). Book 6-8 weeks in advance, earlier for summer birthdays.",
